c: 5
v: 75
t: "Masiya mutabani wa Mariam tali kintu kirala kyonna okugyako okuba nti Mubaka wa Katonda era nga ddala ababaka bangi abaamukulembera, ne Maama we yali Mukazi omukkiriza ow'amazima bombi baalyanga emmere, tunula olabe engeri gyetubannyonnyolamu ebigambo ate tunula olabe engeri gyebawugulwa"